  <brief_title>Vision Restoration With a Collagen Crosslinked Boston Keratoprosthesis Unit</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I/II Prospective, Randomized, Multicenter, Double-Masked, Vehicle-Controlled Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Corneal Collagen Cross-Linking of Keratoprosthesis Carrier Tissue in High-Risk Keratoprosthesis Implantation</official_title>
